{"tid":641684,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我在交友apps認識的她（真人真事）","createTime":"2018-04-25T07:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T07:34:40.000Z","uid":162644,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"19a8f4e7c5b4f74af7be9f2261bd4639ced6422f","tid":641684,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"第一次寫文，d正字撚高抬貴手<br />\n<br />\n首先簡單交待下自己背景<br />\n五官正常未到靚仔但絕對唔係樣衰<br />\n有做gym，著衫已經睇得出。<br />\n<br />\n雖然自己唔算十分毒係學校都會同女仔有講有笑<br />\n但我都係中意玩交友apps識女仔，一方面避免面對面既尷尬，另一方面唔洗怕dead air<br />\ntinxxx,sayxx ,遇x,skoxx,你講得出我都可能玩過。<br />\n<br />\n男仔玩apps通常都係為左約炮，<br />\n尤其自己有少少條件真係唔難搵<br />\n今日tinxxx忽然彈左個配對成功既信息出黎<br />\n我入去一睇，個名叫做「等待著你」<br />\n而且重係用愛情語錄個d相做profile picture <br />\n所以我都已經唔想add佢<br />\n<br />\n點知過左陣，tinxxx彈左個信息出黎<br />\n無錯，就係「等待著你」sd過黎<br />\n而佢第一句說話就係：hi,你睇落都幾大隻喎<br />\n咩料？第一句就咁講野<br />\n有玩開apps既巴打都應該知有野玩<br />\n我乘住個勢講：多謝喎，但我又見唔到你張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n言語間不足五句我已經拎左佢wtsapp<br />\n到我一加佢wtsapp時候<br />\n點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n待續，有野做緊反應好再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d38481edd5f3268d0cc730c8beeabdbf97a1fb","tid":641684,"uid":71712,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"講你就講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf47df593578cecd3cfc0852f66161286cde552","tid":641684,"uid":49298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"快撚啲出啦"},{"pid":"e07bc5e608f2bf80a5a85519967ed8bf2009538c","tid":641684,"uid":99836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"快撚d啦 情聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bed3a48d5f61e042e8e064f8acb4e013c53d79c","tid":641684,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:20:34